sources.description: Title: Docks of San Francisco Summary: Barbary Coast, San Francisco. The gangster moll Belle gets deeply entangled with gangsters led by her boyfriend Vance. The professional writer John Banning understands why Belle got ... Directed by: George B. Seitz Actors: Production Company: Ralph M. Like Productions Release Date: 1 February 1932 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 Barbary Coast, San Francisco. The gangster moll Belle gets deeply entangled with gangsters led by her boyfriend Vance. The professional writer John Banning understands why Belle got involved with these criminals. Banning tries to help her get out of that seedy life. However, It is not easy. A lot of action and violence ensues before Belle eventually succeeds.
